    "controller_support": "full",
    "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3911490/extras/86c5d0d4ae49fcdd2b0ebab14931e89c.avif?t=1766415224\" width=800 height=102 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Un juego por turnos que fusiona la construcción de mazos con el combate táctico. Moldea tus runas en formaciones letales, encadena combos devastadores y abréte paso a través de mazmorras ancestrales para enfrentar a las oscuras fuerzas que acechan en las profundidades.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">     <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3911490/extras/4e78cbedec59242ce377b88440ee4ddf.avif?t=1766415224\" width=650 height=106 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Juega, intercambia y mueve tus runas para desatar poderosos combos de tres en línea. Un campo de batalla persistente te permite planificar no solo el turno actual, sino también estratégicas jugadas futuras.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3911490/extras/9ec8583971e8eb09fbdab33edbd07ded.poster.avif?t=1766415224\" width=800 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3911490/extras/9ec8583971e8eb09fbdab33edbd07ded.webm?t=1766415224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3911490/extras/9ec8583971e8eb09fbdab33edbd07ded.mp4?t=1766415224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3911490/extras/7d24a53b9ab721e8b87f1e13635abda6.avif?t=1766415224\" width=650 height=106 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Encadena tus runas con intención para destrozar a tus enemigos. A medida que avanzas hacia las profundidades de la mazmorra, cada encuentro pone a prueba tu estrategia y habilidad, enfrentándote a enemigos cada vez más oscuros y retorcidos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3911490/extras/2035318caa23bf23355cfb5eb2bc23f5.poster.avif?t=1766415224\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3911490/extras/2035318caa23bf23355cfb5eb2bc23f5.webm?t=1766415224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3911490/extras/2035318caa23bf23355cfb5eb2bc23f5.mp4?t=1766415224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3911490/extras/03bba8769cd588ffeb100a458680499b.avif?t=1766415224\" width=650 height=106 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ajusta rápidamente tu mazo antes de cada combate. Opta por un mazo reducido y enfocado en sinergias de eliminación, o por uno más grande que otorgue poderosas bonificaciones.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3911490/extras/f8843fb04438bee37458450bd3ce9b81.poster.avif?t=1766415224\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3911490/extras/f8843fb04438bee37458450bd3ce9b81.webm?t=1766415224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3911490/extras/f8843fb04438bee37458450bd3ce9b81.mp4?t=1766415224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3911490/extras/c3bbe2b2dd2f1748057677a85993e997.avif?t=1766415224\" width=650 height=106 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forja tu camino fortaleciendo y duplicando tus runas. Descubre tesoros y artefactos en un mundo donde cada aventura es única.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3911490/extras/912952d4ff65a846aaf0867115592576.poster.avif?t=1766415224\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3911490/extras/912952d4ff65a846aaf0867115592576.webm?t=1766415224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3911490/extras/912952d4ff65a846aaf0867115592576.mp4?t=1766415224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3911490/extras/fad18e51ef2eb9a755e53c6ae9b90c86.avif?t=1766415224\" width=650 height=106 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mejora a tu héroe, desbloquea habilidades permanentes para potenciar tus futuras incursiones. Mientras tanto, la dificultad de la mazmorra se ajusta dinámicamente, presentando un reto tanto para novatos como para veteranos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3911490/extras/c5413f00ac147fe304d8548e487b928a.poster.avif?t=1766415224\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3911490/extras/c5413f00ac147fe304d8548e487b928a.webm?t=1766415224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3911490/extras/c5413f00ac147fe304d8548e487b928a.mp4?t=1766415224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Prueba la DEMO GRATUITA</strong> y experimenta el capítulo introductorio de la aventura, que incluye:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >El primer personaje jugable: <i>Fénix</i>, con un mazo de 60 runas.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >El Acto 1, con 7 combates.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20 enemigos únicos.</p></li>[]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sistema completo de mejora de personaje.</p>[/][]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Soporte completo para mandos.</p>[/]</ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3911490/extras/6fa747a0e5a70a487febc7aa4b101ae3.avif?t=1766415224\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3911490/extras_big/6fa747a0e5a70a487febc7aa4b101ae3.webp?t=1766415224 width=1600 height=659 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
    "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3911490/extras/86c5d0d4ae49fcdd2b0ebab14931e89c.avif?t=1766415224\" width=800 height=102 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Un juego por turnos que fusiona la construcción de mazos con el combate táctico. Moldea tus runas en formaciones letales, encadena combos devastadores y abréte paso a través de mazmorras ancestrales para enfrentar a las oscuras fuerzas que acechan en las profundidades.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">     <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3911490/extras/4e78cbedec59242ce377b88440ee4ddf.avif?t=1766415224\" width=650 height=106 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Juega, intercambia y mueve tus runas para desatar poderosos combos de tres en línea. Un campo de batalla persistente te permite planificar no solo el turno actual, sino también estratégicas jugadas futuras.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3911490/extras/9ec8583971e8eb09fbdab33edbd07ded.poster.avif?t=1766415224\" width=800 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3911490/extras/9ec8583971e8eb09fbdab33edbd07ded.webm?t=1766415224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3911490/extras/9ec8583971e8eb09fbdab33edbd07ded.mp4?t=1766415224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai