de la mazmorra se ajusta dinámicamente, presentando un reto tanto para novatos como para veteranos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3911490/extras/c5413f00ac147fe304d8548e487b928a.poster.avif?t=1766415224\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3911490/extras/c5413f00ac147fe304d8548e487b928a.webm?t=1766415224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3911490/extras/c5413f00ac147fe304d8548e487b928a.mp4?t=1766415224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Prueba la DEMO GRATUITA</strong> y experimenta el capítulo introductorio de la aventura, que incluye:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >El primer personaje jugable: <i>Fénix</i>, con un mazo de 60 runas.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >El Acto 1, con 7 combates.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20 enemigos únicos.</p></li>[]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sistema completo de mejora de personaje.</p>[/][]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Soporte completo para mandos.</p>[/]</ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3911490/extras/6fa747a0e5a70a487febc7aa4b101ae3.avif?t=1766415224\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3911490/extras_big/6fa747a0e5a70a487febc7aa4b101ae3.webp?t=1766415224 width=1600 height=659 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
